                        Amet minim mollit non deserunt ullamco est sit aliqua dolor do amet sint. Velit officia consequat duis enim velit mollit. Exercitation veniam consequat.
                    </p>
                    <div class="mt-10 sm:flex sm:items-center sm:space-x-8">
                        <a href="#" title="Start exploring" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-200 bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 focus:bg-orange-600" role="button">
                            Start exploring
